				<h2>Train Ticket Generator</h2>
				<p><strong>Brief:</strong> A user will be able to generate a train ticket based on train data saved to an Oracle SQL database. A form is dynamically created based on the number of passengers, and the final ticket is saved to the user's Downloads folder.</p>
				<p><strong>The goal</strong> for this project was to create a simple web application using Java, JSP, Oracle SQL, and JavaScript.</p>
